com.interpss.core.aclf

Interface AclfNetwork

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseAclfNetwork<AclfBus,AclfBranch>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAreaZone, IAclfNetAdjustment, IAclfNetElement, IAclfNetFormMatrix, IAclfNetFunc, IAclfNetLookup, IChildNet, INet3WXfrElement, NameTag, Network<AclfBus,AclfBranch>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PlanningAclfNetwork
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfNetworkImpl, PlanningAclfNetworkImpl

    public interface AclfNetwork
extends BaseAclfNetwork<AclfBus,AclfBranch>, IAclfNetLookup
    A representation of the model object 'Network'. AclfNetwork class is for storing network information for implementing AC loadflow analysis.

    The following features are supported:

    • Has Equiv Gen Load
    • Equiv Gen Load Cache
    • Flow Interface Loaded
    • Flow Interface List
    See Also:
    AclfPackage.getAclfNetwork()
